NOTE: This module is best viewed as a rendered html. A pre-print version is available here: https://kgfitzgerald.github.io/baylor_apu_score/baseball/mlb_prime_age/. You can also render the html locally by first opening mlb_prime_age.Rproj to launch RStudio, then open index.qmd and click "Render".

This repository contains files for a SCORE module on MLB player's prime age. 

index.qmd: primary Quarto document that renders the Module itself (including facilitation notes and student instructions).

student_template.qmd: Quarto file to be provided to students, where they will type their code and answers

batter_stats.csv: cleaned version of data originally pulled in May 2024 using the fg_batter_leaders() function from the baseballs package. Ten seasons 2014-2023 included.


pitcher_stats.csv: cleaned version of data originally pulled in May 2024 using the fg_pitcher_leaders() function from the baseballs package. Ten seasons 2014-2023 included.


styles.css: adjusts html viewing layout for index.qmd

baseball_WAR_shiny_app folder contains files that produce the Shiny app embedded at the end of the module. App hosted at https://kgfitz.shinyapps.io/Baseball_WAR/

